Control Resource IndustriesInc said it named R. Joseph Clancy as president.    R. Steven Lutterbach, who previously held the president'stitle, continues as chairman and chief executive officer.    Clancy was a vice president and member of the board ofdirectors.    The company also named Cody Geddes as vice president andchief financial officer, succeeding John Wojcik, who remains asexecutive vice president. Reuter&#3;